<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 03:27:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国2月的制造业活动达到三个月高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-february-manufacturing-activity-hits-three-month-high-2025-03-01/</link><description>工厂的一项正式调查显示，中国的制造业活动于2月份恢复了，周六的一项正式调查表明，北京的刺激措施正在帮助造成世界第二大经济体的零散恢复。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 01:51:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-february-manufacturing-activity-hits-three-month-high-2025-03-01/</guid></item><item><title>Bessent说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-has-proposed-matching-us-tariffs-china-bessent-says-2025-02-28/</link><description>美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）周五表示，墨西哥提议将美国对中国的关税匹配，以此他称其为“非常有趣”，而加拿大应该匹配。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 21:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-has-proposed-matching-us-tariffs-china-bessent-says-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>CMA CGM说，美国港口的港口费将影响所有运输公司。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-port-fees-china-vessels-would-affect-all-shipping-firms-cma-cgm-says-2025-02-28/</link><description>总部位于法国的运输公司CMA CGM周五表示，美国提出撞到港口费用高的中国船只的提议将对集装箱运输行业的所有公司产生重大影响，其中大多数船只是在中国建造的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 16:29:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-port-fees-china-vessels-would-affect-all-shipping-firms-cma-cgm-says-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>财政部长敦促加拿大，墨西哥加拿大，随着截止日期迫在眉睫的范围</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-canada-seek-forestall-trumps-tariffs-with-anti-drug-efforts-2025-02-28/</link><description>美国财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）周五鼓励加拿大跟随墨西哥，以符合美国对中国商品的关税，因为美国两位邻国试图避免在周二因芬太尼贩运而惩罚25％的美国关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 16:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-canada-seek-forestall-trumps-tariffs-with-anti-drug-efforts-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>习近平说，中国和俄罗斯应该加强国际事务的协调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-should-strengthen-coordination-international-affairs-xi-says-2025-02-28/</link><description>据中国州媒体报道，中国媒体上周五在北京说，中国和俄罗斯需要继续加强国际和地区事务的协调。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 12:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-should-strengthen-coordination-international-affairs-xi-says-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>一些外国人从缅甸骗局中心撤出面对回家的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/some-foreigners-pulled-out-myanmar-scam-centres-face-struggle-get-home-2025-02-28/</link><description>两名被拘留者说，在犯罪团伙经营的中心的镇压中，数百名外国国民从缅甸的骗局中撤出，在他们被带到偏远的民兵营中，几乎没有食物，医疗保健和肮脏的厕所很少。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 12:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/some-foreigners-pulled-out-myanmar-scam-centres-face-struggle-get-home-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责英国寻求抹黑其新疆政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-accuses-uk-seeking-discredit-its-xinjiang-policy-2025-02-28/</link><description>伦敦大使馆发言人说，英国正试图抹黑中国西北部地区的政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 11:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-accuses-uk-seeking-discredit-its-xinjiang-policy-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国大使馆在Uyghurs驱逐出国后在泰国发出安全警报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-embassy-issues-security-alert-thailand-after-uyghurs-deportation-china-2025-02-28/</link><description>美国大使馆周五在曼谷驻曼谷大使馆为其在泰国的公民发出了安全警报。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 10:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-embassy-issues-security-alert-thailand-after-uyghurs-deportation-china-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国要求自动驾驶软件升级的监管部门批准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-mandates-regulatory-approvals-autonomous-driving-software-upgrades-2025-02-28/</link><description>中国行业部周五表示，与自动驾驶相关的空中软件升级将受到监管批准的约束，这是旨在防止汽车制造商隐藏缺陷或避免责任的新法规的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 10:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-mandates-regulatory-approvals-autonomous-driving-software-upgrades-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国删除工业部的共产党酋长金·宗隆（Jin Zhuanglong）</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-industry-ministrys-communist-party-chief-jin-zhuanglong-2025-02-28/</link><description>根据周五的一份部门声明，金宗隆（Jin Zhuanglong）是中国航空航天部门的重要名称，被从该国行业部的共产党秘书任职。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 08:57:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-industry-ministrys-communist-party-chief-jin-zhuanglong-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：所谓的中国间谍给菲律宾市和警察现金和摩托车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-chinese-spies-gave-philippine-city-police-cash-motorbikes-2025-02-28/</link><description>路透社看到的照片，视频和在线帖子中，菲律宾指控菲律宾的四名国民向中国共产党附属团体捐款，向菲律宾城市捐款，并向两名警察部队捐款。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 08:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-chinese-spies-gave-philippine-city-police-cash-motorbikes-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国银行正在降低美元存款的利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-banks-heed-pboc-call-cut-dollar-deposit-rates-say-sources-2025-02-28/</link><description>消息人士称，中国的银行在中央银行要求这样做后，削减了美元存款的利率，可能会减少ho积美元，并支撑较弱的人民币。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 06:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-banks-heed-pboc-call-cut-dollar-deposit-rates-say-sources-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚批评泰国驱逐出中国的Uyghurs</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticises-thailands-deportation-uyghurs-china-2025-02-28/</link><description>澳大利亚外交部长潘妮·王（Penny Wong）周五表示，澳大利亚与泰国的决定违背了他们的意愿将40个Uyghurs转移到中国，并引起了他们对中国政府的待遇的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 05:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticises-thailands-deportation-uyghurs-china-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>Tass报道说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-russian-security-official-holds-beijing-talks-with-chinese-foreign-minister-2025-02-28/</link><description>俄罗斯安全委员会的秘书谢尔盖·肖古（Sergei Shoigu）周五在俄罗斯TASS州新闻社上会见了中国总统习近平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 05:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-russian-security-official-holds-beijing-talks-with-chinese-foreign-minister-2025-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>在最新的关税威胁之后，中国指责我们芬太尼“勒索”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-opposes-latest-us-tariff-threat-2025-02-28/</link><description>特朗普威胁要对中国进口的10％额外承担10％的责任。</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 05:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-opposes-latest-us-tariff-threat-2025-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>